WEBVTT

00:00:01.875 --> 00:00:04.601
The world today has many problems.

00:00:04.625 --> 00:00:10.143
And they're all very complicated
and interconnected and difficult.

00:00:10.167 --> 00:00:12.601
But there is something we can do.

00:00:12.625 --> 00:00:13.893
I believe

00:00:13.917 --> 00:00:18.684
that girls' education is the closest thing
we have to a silver bullet

00:00:18.708 --> 00:00:23.101
to help solve some of the world's
most difficult problems.

00:00:23.125 --> 00:00:25.226
But you don't have to take my word for it.

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:26.934
The World Bank says

00:00:26.958 --> 00:00:30.226
that girls' education
is one of the best investments